00:28:07.880 --> 00:28:09.880
'Adalah salah memikirkan semua ini.'

00:28:10.320 --> 00:28:13.160
'Aku tidak akan pernah memikirkan hal ini.'

00:28:33.720 --> 00:28:34.840 line:20%
'Tanda tangani ini.'

00:28:37.480 --> 00:28:39.960 line:20%
"Kami ingin ini
membatalkan pernikahanmu."

00:28:41.760 --> 00:28:44.040 line:20%
'Tunggu apa lagi,
Jhanak?  Tanda tangani.'

00:28:45.400 --> 00:28:47.320 line:20%
'Aniruddha, bahkan kamu.'

00:28:49.280 --> 00:28:50.520 line:20%
'Tanda tangan!'